citations:
    citation-asos-catelyn-i:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Catelyn I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Catelyn confined to Hoster Tully's chambers at Riverrun after freeing Jaime. Hoster Tully delirious, calling for 'Tansy' and begging forgiveness. Catelyn deduces Lord Hoster forced Lysa to abort a pregnancy (by Petyr Baelish) before marrying Jon Arryn. Edmure returns from battle with news of Stannis's defeat at King's Landing."
